text: She'll Take Romance (alternate title: I'll Take Romance) is a 1990 American television comedy movie directed by Piers Haggard and starring Linda Evans, Tom Skerritt, Heather Tom, DeLane Matthews, Larry Poindexter. ==Other websites== * Category:1990 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Television movies Category:Movies directed by Piers Haggard Category:Movies set in Seattle
